{"tid":292056,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"HBO拍Watchmen電視劇","createTime":"2017-06-21T05:01:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T05:29:29.000Z","uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"484afcb112c93a19e25323680f7530015d9277da","tid":292056,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:01:08.000Z","msg":"繼先前已經被搬上大銀幕的DC漫畫英雄系列《守護者/Watchmen》，接下來我們將會重新以HBO影集的方式看到他們了！！<br />\n<br />\n找來了HBO現以完結的影集《末世餘生/The Leftovers》編劇「戴蒙林德洛夫/Damon Lindelof」擔任主要製作，林德洛夫過去曾參與過知名ABC懸疑影集《迷失/Lost》還有異形前傳《普羅米修斯》等作品的編導，根據 Variety新聞的消息指出，這部新的守護者影集不會跟原本DC電影宇宙有連結，而是一個全新獨立的世界觀。<br />\n<br />\n結合了HBO影集高接受度的特色，守護者的影集能拜託多數英雄電影與影集的限制，更真實的呈現原作品中反應人性的畫面與內容，而且這次我們將會看到的故事不再跟先前一樣需要被擠進一個三小時的冗長電影中，反而編劇們有足夠的空間來好好的訴說一個故事，希望這次的新作能夠帶給觀眾更多原作者「艾倫莫爾/Alan Moore」想要傳達的訊息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://geek-base.toy-people.com/?p=1006\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgeek-base.toy-people.com%2F%3Fp%3D1006&d=8eAG5A1w8i1IXExU1jg3cGxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=504cac52\" target=\"_blank\">https://geek-base.toy-people.com/?p=1006</a>"},{"pid":"f4e108297866529fce8b634dbbb97f0a53865144","tid":292056,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:04:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4d9b6ba5f63c320025cfd3be7b291f5de148c3c","tid":292056,"uid":51348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:09:12.000Z","msg":"咁撚正？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f950169bac3f121454205031c939e946e3aa4bc6","tid":292056,"uid":10626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agre